data.description:
LETS SCHEDULE A SHOWING. Introducing a captivating lake view home nestled in the heart of Riss Lake, Parkville, Missouri. Do you like updates? How about new carpet in the fully finished walkout basement? How about fresh touch-up paint throughout the house? How about updated appliances in the kitchen? As you step inside, be greeted by the allure of the open floor plan seamlessly uniting the spaces. The main-level master suite is a haven of tranquility, providing a sitting area by the gas fireplace with unparalleled views of Riss Lake. Immerse yourself in the spa-like bathrooms, with tiled floors and showers a sanctuary of relaxation and elegance.
Boasting 5 oversized bedrooms, a children’s play area, and newer carpet on the upper level. Offering 4.5 bathrooms making getting ready for school a breeze. The master bathroom is a spa like oasis making your daily routines a refreshing experience. The hearth room offers a family gathering area while staying connected with the chef in kitchen. The kitchen offers an island to make the morning breakfast an inviting ritual and endless counter space for your culinary desires.
The walkout finished basement adds an extra layer of entertainment and functionality to this already splendid home. The new carpet adds a sense of warmth to the enjoyable space and is perfect for entertaining guests.  Check out the fully functional wet bar with full size refrigerator to stock your favorite beverages.  Imagine hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet evenings overlooking the lake from the comfort of your own home. The pool table and furniture is all negotiable. 
This property is not just a house! it's an experience waiting to unfold. Don't miss the opportunity to make this dream home yours. Your lakeside paradise awaits – seize the moment!
